FEB 15th - Get on board The Blues Train! Still a  few tickets available. Such a fun night!! Ticket link here:
https://www.thebluestrain.com.au/show/sat-15-feb-2020/#
Great time at Levantine Sunday. Great place! Thanks to @beautifulmesspresents for the invitation.

SUNDAY AFTERNOON! I am thrilled to be back at Levantine Hill 1pm til.4pm. Glorious views, fine food and wine, stunning location. Join me!

#levantine #levantinehill #beautifulmess #greenhatchblues #stunningviews #greenhills #awardwinning #winery #blues #sundayvibes #sundaydrive #daytrip #yarravalley
TONIGHT! BAND LAUNCH! Beneath Driver Lane! Get down! 9pm - midnight
BAND LAUNCH! Jan 24th, Beneath Driver Lane! 9 til midnight. Come down!
Playing a request - Stevie Ray's 'Lenny' - for my last group of the night. The train was sitting at the platform, but nobody wanted to leave!
Soundcheck on the Blues Train. The beginning of an awesome ride! Still tix for Dec 14th. Get on board!!
Back on the Bellarine Peninsula, playing The Blues Train! A great night awaits!
The Blues Train! December 14th! Grab your tickets now!
FRIDAY NIGHT! The Railyard Saloon! 8pm. Head to the hills!!
Mastering the ep with Master, Rob Dillon. Awesome!
Playing The Railyard in Tecoma next Friday. 8pm. Looking forward to it!
Good vibes goin on Beneath Driver Lane tonight!

A few gigs coming up. 
Nov 9th - Beneath Driver Lane 
Nov 10th - Hop Nation. 
Details soon.
Love Sundays at The Little French Deli. Great place to relax & unwind, soak up some Springtime Blues before beginning a new week. Join me in the Courtyard. 3:30 - 6:30pm

Just 2 months til I'm back aboard the Mighty Blues Train!  Limited tickets available so book now - don't miss out! 
4 carriages. 4 awesome acts. One wild ride! 
Check the link for details. 
https://www.thebluestrain.com.au/artist/greenhatch-blues/
Great night Beneath Driver Lane tonight, jamming with Anna Scionti and surprise guest, Chris Canning, just back after touring Europe. Thanks @annasciontimusic

First up this Friday! BLUES IN THE BASEMENT!! 9pm - midnight 
I'll be jammin on a tune or two with my mate Anna Scionti. Can't wait! Get down!
Sunday! HOP NATION! Cool brewery with chilled vibes for your weekend. Check it out!
Playing this place Saturday night! Awesome venue! Come down for some Blues in the Basement! 9pm
NEXT WEEKEND - looking forward to supporting ISEULA at Beneath Driver Lane. We'll jam on a few tunes during 3rd set. Should be a great night! SATURDAY 14th SEPTEMBER. 9pm. Join us!

All aboard! Get your tickets for The Blues Train! Always an awesome night, whoever's playing! 
I have a couple of shows coming up in December, but check the website to see the Spring Lineup. Best way to shake off those winter blues!! .
https://www.thebluestrain.com.au/
